"      Blanco F, Frasson M, Flor-Lorente B, et al. Solitary rectal ulcer: ultrasonographic and magnetic resonance imaging patterns mimicking rectal cancer. Eur J Gastroenterol Hepatol 2011; 23:1262.",
"     </a>",
