"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 498px; height: 418px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The foreskin can sometimes get stuck below the head of the penis. This is called &ldquo;paraphimosis.&rdquo; If this happens to you or your son, do not try to force the skin to move. Go to a hospital emergency room for treatment. If this problem is not treated right away, it can cause permanent damage.",
